Gold Price in Hong Kong Up
HONG KONG , December 28 ( Xinhua ) -- The gold price in Hong Kong rose eight HK dollars to close at 2,649 HK dollars a tael on Monday , according to Po Sang Bank , one of the major gold dealers in Hong Kong .
The gold price is equivalent to 287.10 U.S. dollars a troy ounce , 0.90 U.S. dollar up from the previous close at Monday 's exchange rate of one U.S. dollar against 7.7451 HK dollars .
